parameters: I think it's the first time I went to school with my friends
我好像还是第一次和朋友一起上学呢
Everyone is working hard to prepare
大家都在很努力的准备呢…
Although it is tempting to play all the games
虽然很想把全部摊位都玩一遍
But let's get the chalkboard painted first!
但是还是先把黑板报画了吧！
After today's painting tomorrow will be able to play enough ~
今天画完明天就能玩个够了~

parameters.en: Go back to the classroom and draw the blackboard!

parameters: en = Go back to the classroom and draw the blackboard!
cn = 回课室画黑板报吧！
Welcome to the Anime Club of Yume Sakura high school!
欢迎来到梦樱高校漫研部！
Do you want to have a look at the great work that took us a year to complete!
要看一看我们耗时一年完成的巨著吗！
《修普诺斯晚宴》终于要发布了吗！
So we prepared something more powerful
所以我们准备了更厉害的东西！
看来这位同学很感兴趣嘛
This is the wisdom of our Anime Club!
这可是我们漫研部的智慧结晶！
But I really want to have a look
但是我真的好想看一看
No one can refuse the lovely cat girl!
没有人能拒绝可爱的猫娘！
Sorry, there seems to be a problem with this one. It's blank
不好意思，这本好像有点问题，里面是空白的
因为…抱得猫娘归的办法…
Because… marry with cat girl… It's impossible ahhhhhhh
因为…抱得猫娘归的办法…根本就不存在啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊
Why can't I marry the cat girl！！？ Why！
为什么没有能抱得猫娘归的办法！！？为什么！
But the school festival has just begun
但是学园祭不是才刚开始吗
That's why we need to rest
We are exercising every day, so we should have a good rest today
我们天天都在运动，所以学园祭应该好好休息了
This is an ancient continent, named Cabres.
这是一片名叫卡布雷斯的远古大陆。
You ultimately settled down and became a staff for an antique shop.
你最终还是安定下来，并成为了一家古董店的职员。
Shortly after, an ancient demons tribe invaded the continent of Cabres.
不久之后，一个古老的魔族入侵了卡布雷斯大陆。
One day, they came to ransack your workplace.
有一天，魔族来洗劫你工作的地方。
The war with the demons lasted 20 years，the continent of Cabres became scorched earth.
与魔族的战争持续了20年之久，卡布雷斯大陆成为了焦土。
Both sides gave up on the war and flew to outer space using spacecraft looking for a new habitat.
交战双方都放弃了战斗，乘坐飞船飞向了外太空寻找新的栖息地。
Why don't you go to the Anime Club?
Welcome to the Literature Club's game booth!
欢迎来到文学部游戏摊！
Ah~ Since you're here at our booth…
啊~既然你来到了我们的摊位…
You're most likely someone that likes reading books!
想必你也是喜欢看书的人吧！
Then please take a look at our medieval scientific fantasy-themed！
那么请看我们的中古科幻魔幻故事！

我要学园祭正式开始前再钻研一下

Hi, I want to try my new learned secret Takoyaki - Koga Style Takoyaki!

|章鱼烧店铺老板 Takoyaki Shop Owner
(Woah! So many green onions and so much mayonnaise!)
(Wow, the exact right amount of salt, and it tastes so refreshing! Definitely worthy of a secret!)
(哇哦，如此的咸香清爽！不愧是秘传！)

|棉花糖店铺老板 Marshmallow Store Owner

但是为什么不提前准备好呢

这网的质量好像太差了点…
|捞金鱼店铺老板 Goldfish Scooping Shop Owner
It will be damaged as soon as it meets water…
May, are you also in the K-ON club?
小梅你也是轻音部的吗？

啊…不是的，我是偶像研究部的

那为什么你在轻音部的摊位
Their dolls have disappeared, so I help them look after the stalls first
她们的人偶服不见了，所以我帮他们先看着摊位
她们什么时候才回来啊…
